# Ignore native/generated files in language stats
android/** linguist-vendored
ios/** linguist-vendored
build/** linguist-vendored
*.cpp linguist-vendored
*.h linguist-vendored
*.a linguist-vendored
*.so linguist-vendored

# Prioritize Dart for language detection
*.dart linguist-detectable
lib/** linguist-detectable

# Ignore CMake files
**/CMakeLists.txt linguist-generated
*.cmake linguist-generated

# Make sure Dart files are counted
*.dart linguist-detectable
